{"tid":2487200,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係喺果嗰岩啱左咗地哋既嘅有乜分別？","createTime":"2021-04-13T11:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T12:23:40.000Z","uid":368088,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0602fb2fdbd0b7824e7d8975387bddf61ebc547b","tid":2487200,"uid":368088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">係有好撚大分別</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">係</span>hai6<br />\n意思：是<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">喺</span>hai2<br />\n意思：在<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n我係香港人<br />\n我喺香港<br />\n<del>我係香港</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正嘅我係香港：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWG5qPeJCNYdr3SnuvpWuQShuBkJwQHRC2gosgCnwhE4L?filename=AccfyYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAccfyYY.jpg&h=435847de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">果</span>gwo2<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.某些植物花落後含有種子的部分：果實。果品。果木、結果（ａ．結出果實；ｂ．事情的結局或成效）<br />\n2.結局，與&ldquo;因&rdquo;相對：因果、成果<br />\n3.堅決：果決、果斷<br />\n4.確實，真的：果真<br />\n5.充實，飽足：果腹<br />\n6.姓<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">嗰</span>go2<br />\n意思：那個<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n嗰個菠蘿好好食，結果我食咗成個<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>果個菠蘿好好食，結果我食咗成個</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果子狸？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW68VPoTiVGsk8f3i4q6nupynyH1RaJ8brATBA6oAdTV5?filename=1HBDxic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HBDxic.jpg&h=751a4515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">岩</span>ngaam4<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.高峻的山崖：岩壁、岩壑<br />\n2.構成地殼的石頭：岩石、岩洞、岩漿<br />\n3.險要，險峻：岩險、岩邑<br />\n4.山洞：中空成岩、岩居穴處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">啱</span>ngaam1<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.合；合適：呢種款式啱心水（這種款式合她的心意）。我講兩句，唔知啱唔啱（我說兩句，不知道合適不合適）<br />\n2.對；行；可以：你講得啱（你說得對）啱啦（行，可以）<br />\n3.恰巧；剛好：佢咁啱撞到個老友（他恰巧碰到一個老朋友）<br />\n4.才；剛：啱啱食完飯（剛吃完飯）<br />\n5.合得來：佢同啲同學好啱（他和同學們很合得來）<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n我啱啱食完飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>我岩岩食完飯</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你食嘅係岩石？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme5LnP9KVwbCbar2ym45E7gJdv7amuEJAk9W9DFaMmu1c?filename=L4RcBzG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4RcBzG.jpg&h=3cde3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">左</span>zo2<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.面向南時，東的一邊，與&ldquo;右&rdquo;相對：左手、左方、左右、左膀右臂。<br />\n2.地理上指東方：山左、江左<br />\n3.指政治思想上進步或超過現實條件許可的過頭思想和行動：左派、左翼、左傾<br />\n4.斜，偏，差錯：左脾氣、左嗓子<br />\n5.降低官職：左遷<br />\n6.古同&ldquo;佐&rdquo;，佐證<br />\n7.姓<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">咗</span>zo2<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.表示完結，結束<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n你食咗飯未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>我食左飯</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇食埋右？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd7KbxobZJ9fCUBLiJWwriqxFAT1J7d7ppn4fRLWaDh8r?filename=QXxWiWp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXxWiWp.gif&h=31b3565f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">地</span>dei6<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.人類生長活動的所在：地球（太陽系九大行星之一）。地心說。<br />\n2.地球或地球的某部分：地質、地殼<br />\n3.地球表面除去海洋、江河、湖泊的部分：陸地、地下<br />\n4.地球表面的土壤：土地、田地、地政、地主<br />\n5.地球上的一個區域：地區、此地<br />\n6.建築材料鋪成的平面：地板。地毯<br />\n7.所在空間或區域的部位：地點、目的地<br />\n8.人在社會關係中所處的位置：易地以處<br />\n9.表示思想或行動的某種活動領域：見地、境地、心地<br />\n10.底子：質地<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">哋</span>dei6<br />\n意思：<br />\n們：我哋、你哋<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n我哋幾時食飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>我地幾時食飯？</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正嘅我地／你地／佢地：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSx6xvXL5F3Ai7MXSb2YsMafaLHTsC9SWuzbiVKk6hW69?filename=DJm0LxT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJm0LxT.png&h=77e26e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">既</span>gei3<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.動作已經完了：既往不咎、既而<br />\n2.已經：既成事實、既定<br />\n3.常與&ldquo;且&rdquo;、&ldquo;又&rdquo;連用，表示兩者並列：既快又好<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">嘅</span>ge3<br />\n意思：<br />\n1.的，表示領有或修飾關係：我嘅書。<br />\n2.語氣詞，的，一般用於陳述句尾表示強調：佢做事好負責嘅<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n我嘅飯呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>我既飯呢？</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<del><span class=\"small\">樓主未食飯諗唔到圖/gif </span></del><br />\n<br />\nP牌跪求大家打返啱啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊守護我哋嘅母語<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lucky.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fd12cce26f33bd88b4b865479f72dd4f43b65d","tid":2487200,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a4c2e06d250ae0c505ef407bf15e7bf70c699ba4","tid":2487200,"uid":368088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"Btw 求推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7d1e4b5a099a357b87391df0d9d51d33f8b2e8","tid":2487200,"uid":155815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a4a7fbfd06b41ebe1c08d169afaf1a2a9e4e6f","tid":2487200,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike