:"2021-04-13T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n都唔係無用嘅"},{"pid":"ae73ccd27f43c5583c15114696db58a4a7bd3f02","tid":2487200,"uid":211262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"岩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd524c3f1910b3ad3c35b41365f6711b6c986d8e","tid":2487200,"uid":158886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"a9a2c01679984cd76ba0c6ca8ce4bb180ec35247","tid":2487200,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"速成撚不願面對正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗快就乜都可以捨棄<br />\n<br />\nPinyin撚就唔該喺香港消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}